//! Phase 4 three-point frozen region moments.
//!
//! Generated by `cargo run -p halcyon-quote --bin gen_moments_3pt`.
//! DO NOT EDIT MANUALLY.
//!
//! At each (obs_rel, node_idx, μ_ref) the triple `(probability,
//! expectation_u, expectation_v)` is precomputed for both the autocall
//! and KI-safe triangles. The on-chain filter uses
//! `select_frozen_moment_3pt` to pick the μ_ref closest to the current
//! node's `(mean_u, mean_v)` by L¹ distance.

